title: Two story 3 bed/ 2.5 bath for rent
posting_body: ['Nice two story house built in 2008 close Vacaville for rent.', 'Features:', '- 3 bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms', '- Carpet floors', '- Washer/dryer hookup in garage', '- Good size backyard', '- Parking in garage and driveway', '- Close to Vacaville', 'Rental Terms:', '- Minimum one year lease', '- Rent: $2,800 per month', '- Security deposit: $3,000', '- No pets, smoking, or subletting', 'Application Requirements:', '- Most current 2 months paystub', '- 2 months most recent bank statement', '- Current credit and background check require ($42/Adult)', '- Photo ID of each applicant', '- Completed tenant application (with references)', 'If interested, please send introduction about yourself and other occupants, reason for looking, and move in date.', 'Thank you']
